MET


Description

Hepatocyte growth factor receptor (MET). Receptor tyrosine kinase that transduces signals from the extracellular matrix into the cytoplasm by binding to hepatocyte growth factor/HGF ligand.

NCT03638206 - Colorectal Cancer, Esophagus Cancer, Renal Carcinoma, Hepatoma, Lung Cancer, Mesothelioma, Ovarian Cancer, Pancreatic Cancer, Melanoma
NCT03672305 - Hepatoma
